---
// Modalidades .ey-mod - reconstrução fiel
---

<section class="ey-mod" id="modalidades" aria-labelledby="modalidadesTitle">
  <div class="ey-mod__container">

    <header class="ey-mod__header">
      <div class="ey-mod-reveal">
        <p class="ey-mod__eyebrow">Modalidades</p>
        <h2 class="ey-mod__title" id="modalidadesTitle">
          Práticas pensadas para <em>cada momento</em> da vida
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="ey-mod__intro ey-mod-reveal">
        Independente da idade ou experiência, o Yoga acolhe cada corpo e cada ritmo. Conheça as modalidades disponíveis no Essência.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="ey-mod__grid">

      <article class="ey-mod-card ey-mod-reveal">
        <div class="ey-mod-card__media">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/images/yoga-adultos.webp" alt="Praticante em postura de yoga durante aula para adultos em Sorocaba" decoding="async" width="600" height="375" />
          <span class="ey-mod-card__num">01</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ey-mod-card__body">
          <h3 class="ey-mod-card__title">Yoga Adultos</h3>
          <p class="ey-mod-card__desc">Fortaleça o corpo, alivie o estresse e recarregue as energias. Aulas que equilibram mente e corpo promovendo disposição e bem-estar.</p>
          <a href="#contato" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ey-mod-card__link">Saiba mais</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="ey-mod-card ey-mod-reveal">
        <div class="ey-mod-card__media">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/images/yoga-mamae-bebe.webp" alt="Mãe praticando yoga com bebê no colo em aula do Essência do Yoga" decoding="async" width="600" height="375" />
          <span class="ey-mod-card__num">02</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ey-mod-card__body">
          <h3 class="ey-mod-card__title">Yoga Mamãe & Bebê</h3>
          <p class="ey-mod-card__desc">Um momento especial para fortalecer o vínculo entre mãe e filho. Práticas leves que ajudam na recuperação pós-parto e trazem serenidade.</p>
          <a href="#contato" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ey-mod-card__link">Saiba mais</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="ey-mod-card ey-mod-reveal">
        <div class="ey-mod-card__media">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/images/yoga-kids.webp" alt="Crianças em atividade de yoga kids com movimentos lúdicos" decoding="async" width="600" height="375" />
          <span class="ey-mod-card__num">03</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ey-mod-card__body">
          <h3 class="ey-mod-card__title">Yoga Kids</h3>
          <p class="ey-mod-card__desc">Brincar, respirar e se movimentar com consciência. O Yoga Kids estimula concentração, criatividade e equilíbrio emocional das crianças.</p>
          <a href="#contato" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ey-mod-card__link">Saiba mais</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="ey-mod-card ey-mod-reveal">
        <div class="ey-mod-card__media">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/images/yoga-todos.webp" alt="Grupo diverso praticando yoga ao ar livre representando inclusão" decoding="async" width="600" height="375" />
          <span class="ey-mod-card__num">04</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ey-mod-card__body">
          <h3 class="ey-mod-card__title">O Yoga é para Todos</h3>
          <p class="ey-mod-card__desc">Independentemente da idade ou experiência, o Yoga acolhe cada corpo e cada ritmo. Uma prática inclusiva que convida à leveza e à harmonia.</p>
          <a href="#contato" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ey-mod-card__link">Saiba mais</a>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  (function () {
    'use strict';
    const els = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.ey-mod-reveal');
    if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
      const io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
        entries.forEach(function (e) {
          if (e.isIntersecting) {
            e.target.classList.add('is-visible');
            io.unobserve(e.target);
          }
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -30px 0px' });
      els.forEach(function (el, i) {
        el.style.transitionDelay = (i * 70) + 'ms';
        io.observe(el);
      });
    } else {
      els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('is-visible'); });
    }
  })();
</script>

<style>
  .ey-mod {
    --green: #1D603E;
    --green-deep: #154A30;
    --lime: #BEEBAC;
    --lime-pale: #EAF7E4;
    --lilac: #CC6BE6;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --ink: #18241C;
    --ink-soft: #46514A;

    --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;
    --font-sans: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;

    --fs-xs: clamp(0.7rem, 0.68rem + 0.12vw, 0.78rem);
    --fs-sm: clamp(0.82rem, 0.8rem + 0.14vw, 0.92rem);
    --fs-base: clamp(0.95rem, 0.92rem + 0.18vw, 1.05rem);
    --fs-2xl: clamp(2.2rem, 1.5rem + 2.8vw, 3.8rem);

    --gutter: clamp(1.5rem, 1rem + 3vw, 4rem);
    --r-lg: 28px;
    --r-pill: 999px;

    --shadow-soft: 0 4px 20px rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.06);
    --shadow-lg: 0 24px 64px rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.14);
    --ease: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);

    padding: clamp(5rem, 4rem + 5vw, 9rem) 0;
    background: var(--white);
    scroll-margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .ey-mod *,
  .ey-mod *::before,
  .ey-mod *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  .ey-mod__container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--gutter);
  }

  .ey-mod__header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 1rem + 3vw, 4rem);
    align-items: end;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3.5rem, 2.5rem + 3vw, 6rem);
  }

  .ey-mod__eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--lilac) !important;
  }
  .ey-mod__eyebrow::before {
    content: "";
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--lilac);
  }

  .ey-mod__title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--fs-2xl);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink) !important;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }
  .ey-mod__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--green) !important;
  }

  .ey-mod__intro {
    color: var(--ink-soft) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    max-width: 440px;
    justify-self: end;
    font-size: var(--fs-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .ey-mod__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(1.25rem, 1rem + 1vw, 2rem);
  }

  .ey-mod-card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--lime-pale) !important;
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 600ms var(--ease), box-shadow 600ms var(--ease);
  }
  .ey-mod-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .ey-mod-card__media {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ey-mod-card__media img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 1.4s var(--ease);
  }
  .ey-mod-card:hover .ey-mod-card__media img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  .ey-mod-card__media::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 40%, rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.45));
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ey-mod-card__num {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.1rem;
    left: 1.1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #fff !important;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    background: rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.35);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }

  .ey-mod-card__body {
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 1rem + 1vw, 2.25rem);
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ey-mod-card__title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 1.1rem + 0.6vw, 1.65rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink) !important;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .ey-mod-card__desc {
    color: var(--ink-soft) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1.35rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ey-mod-card__link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green) !important;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    margin-top: auto;
    align-self: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ey-mod-card__link::after {
    content: "\2192";
    transition: transform 400ms var(--ease);
  }
  .ey-mod-card__link:hover::after {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }
  .ey-mod-card__link::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--green);
    transition: width 400ms var(--ease);
  }
  .ey-mod-card__link:hover::before {
    width: calc(100% - 1.5rem);
  }

  .ey-mod .ey-mod-reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 800ms var(--ease), transform 800ms var(--ease);
  }
  .ey-mod .ey-mod-reveal.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .ey-mod__header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .ey-mod__intro { justify-self: start; max-width: 100%; }
    .ey-mod__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ey-mod { padding: clamp(3.5rem, 3rem + 2vw, 5rem) 0; }
    .ey-mod-card__body { padding: 1.25rem; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ey-mod .ey-mod-reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .ey-mod-card { transition: none; }
  }
</style>
